@startuml Exercise09-Extend-Swap-LVM-server2
!theme plain
title Exercise 09 — Extend swap LV on server2 (terminal)\n<size:12>vdb → centos9s | swap 2 GiB → 2,5 GiB | vdc/datastore unchanged (ex. 07)</size>

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam BoxPadding 8
skinparam ParticipantPadding 12

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor<<host>> #D6EAF8
  BorderColor<<host>> #2874A6
  BackgroundColor<<vm>> #D5F5E3
  BorderColor<<vm>> #1E8449
  BackgroundColor<<disk>> #FCF3CF
  BorderColor<<disk>> #B7950B
  BackgroundColor<<lvm>> #FDEBD0
  BorderColor<<lvm>> #CA6F1E
  BackgroundColor<<swap>> #FADBD8
  BorderColor<<swap>> #C0392B
  BackgroundColor<<validate>> #E8DAEF
  BorderColor<<validate>> #7D3C98
}

actor "Tu\n(Fedora host)" as Admin <<host>>
participant "server2\nroot CLI" as S2 <<vm>>
participant "/dev/vdb\n(ex-extradisk1)" as VDB <<disk>>
participant "VG centos9s\n(vda2 + vdb)" as VG <<lvm>>
participant "LV swap\n/dev/centos9s/swap" as Swap <<swap>>
participant "validate.sh\n(lab-practice)" as Val <<validate>>

== Estado inicial (lab) ==
note over VDB #FCF3CF
  **vdb**: ext4 montado em **/extradisk1**
end note
note over VG #FDEBD0
  **centos9s** só em **/dev/vda2**
  **0** free PE — swap LV = **2 GiB**
end note
note over VDB #D5F5E3
  **vdc** / **datastore** (ex. 07) — **não mexer**
end note

== A — Libertar vdb ==
Admin -> S2 : ssh / vagrant ssh server2
S2 -> S2 : umount /extradisk1
S2 -> S2 : remover linha extradisk1 em /etc/fstab
S2 -> VDB : wipefs -a /dev/vdb
note right of VDB #FCF3CF
  vdb sem MOUNTPOINT
end note

== B — Dar espaço ao VG do sistema ==
S2 -> VDB : pvcreate /dev/vdb
S2 -> VG : vgextend centos9s /dev/vdb
note over VG #FDEBD0
  **~16 GiB** free PE em centos9s
  (pvs: /dev/vdb → centos9s)
end note

== C — Estender swap LV (+512 MiB) ==
S2 -> Swap : swapoff /dev/centos9s/swap
note over Swap #FADBD8
  swap **desativado** antes do resize
end note
S2 -> Swap : lvextend -L +512M /dev/centos9s/swap
note over Swap #FADBD8
  LV passa a **~2,5 GiB**
  (lvs: swap 2.50g)
end note
S2 -> Swap : mkswap /dev/centos9s/swap
note over Swap #FADBD8
  **Novo UUID** — obrigatório após mkswap
end note
S2 -> Swap : swapon /dev/centos9s/swap
note over Swap #FADBD8
  /proc/swaps ~2621436 KiB
  free -h: Swap **2.5Gi**
end note

== D — Persistência ==
S2 -> S2 : blkid /dev/centos9s/swap
S2 -> S2 : atualizar /etc/fstab (UUID + swap)
S2 -> S2 : swapoff + swapon -a (teste)

== E — Validação no host ==
Admin -> Val : ./scripts/lab-practice.sh validate 09
Val -> S2 : vagrant ssh — pvs, lvs, swapon, fstab
Val --> Admin : **7 OK** — exercício correto

legend right
  | Cor | Camada |
  | <#D6EAF8> | Host / administrador |
  | <#D5F5E3> | VM server2 |
  | <#FCF3CF> | Disco vdb |
  | <#FDEBD0> | LVM volume group |
  | <#FADBD8> | Logical volume swap |
  | <#E8DAEF> | Script de validação |
endlegend

@enduml
